# Fenster-Konfigurator Setup Guide

## Step 1: Create Repository on GitHub
1. Go to github.com/new
2. Create new repository: `fenster-konfigurator`
3. Initialize with README
4. Clone to your machine: `git clone https://github.com/Kostelkarlos1/fenster-konfigurator.git`

